Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}To save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人  \N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}深切懷念托馬斯•梅林\N孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一個存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在阿富汗的時候  我的部隊的任務\N{\b0\fs12}When I was in Afghanistan,, my unit was tasked
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是保護葛雷姆•卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}with protecting Gholem Qadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,販賣鴉片  販賣兒童\N{\b0\fs12}Sold opium. Sold children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得你哥哥是怎麼死的\N{\b0\fs12}How is it you think your brother ended up dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你向一名客戶開槍  但是打偏了\N{\b0\fs12}You shot at a client, you missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我從不會打偏\N{\b0\fs12}I don't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你殺了莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}You murdered Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  扳機是我扣動的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I pulled the trigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你  槍口是你瞄準的\N{\b0\fs12}but you, you aimed the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這裡幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前  我對你做出過一項承諾\N{\b0\fs12}Five years ago, I made you a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你死  直到你瞭解什麼叫徹底絕望\N{\b0\fs12}You cannot die until you have known complete despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你會瞭解的  我向你承諾\N{\b0\fs12}And you will. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,兇手\N{\b0\fs12}Murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[俄語]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你好嗎  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我能幫你什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,星城可沒有古拉格監獄\N{\b0\fs12}There's no Gulags here in Starling City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿納托利話太多\N{\b0\fs12}Anatoly talks too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}Eto verno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你幫我找一個人\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to find a man for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他名叫斯萊德•威爾遜  是個有錢的澳大利亞人\N{\b0\fs12}His name is Slade Wilson. He's rich, Australian,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一隻眼睛瞎了\N{\b0\fs12}and he's missing an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我得知道他睡在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}I need to know where he sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  我需要你幫我的忙\N{\b0\fs12}First, I need your assistance with my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有個人欠我很大一筆錢\N{\b0\fs12}There is a man who owes me a substantial amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來交易的\N{\b0\fs12}I am not here to trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我們的友情是什麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}You know how our brotherhood works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你一個忙\N{\b0\fs12}I do a favor for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你也幫我一個忙\N{\b0\fs12}and you do one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,記在我賬上  阿列克西\N{\b0\fs12}Put it on my tab, Aleksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒時間玩這些遊戲\N{\b0\fs12}I don't have time for these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就騰出時間\N{\b0\fs12}Make time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你對我有用\N{\b0\fs12}My services are of no use to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,否則我不對你提供幫助\N{\b0\fs12}unless yours are use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這種友情是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}I know exactly how this brotherhood works,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  你為我服務\N{\b0\fs12}And right now, it works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我醒來時你已經走了\N{\b0\fs12}I woke up and you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不累\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. I wasn't tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你該累的\N{\b0\fs12}You should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次睡覺是什麼時候\N{\b0\fs12}When's the last time you actually slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在我發現斯萊德•威爾遜還活著之前\N{\b0\fs12}Right before I found out that Slade Wilson is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想談談嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you want to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說\N{\b0\fs12}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我倆都\N{\b0\fs12}I know neither one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不大擅長分享感情\N{\b0\fs12}are very good about sharing our feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我明白\N{\b0\fs12}but...I mean, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  還有...\N{\b0\fs12}Slade, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,事情很多\N{\b0\fs12}And it's a lot, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你害怕也沒關係  我也是\N{\b0\fs12}it's ok if you're scared. I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德回星城是有計劃的\N{\b0\fs12}Slade came back to Starling City with an agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  他想大量生產米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}First, he tries to mass produce the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他出現在\N{\b0\fs12}Then he shows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我母親的家裡\N{\b0\fs12}at my mother's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他想爭鬥  沒問題\N{\b0\fs12}So he wants a fight, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我滿足他  這次\N{\b0\fs12}I'll give him a fight. And this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我殺了他時\N{\b0\fs12}when I kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,會保證他死得透透的\N{\b0\fs12}I will make damn sure that he stays dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是得找到他\N{\b0\fs12}I just need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,熱可哥\N{\b0\fs12}Hot cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有棉花糖嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What, no marshmallows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這裡做什麼  狄格\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here, Dig?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,留神一切\N{\b0\fs12}Keeping an eye on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你說的一切指的是我的脖子吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. And by things, you mean my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得斯萊德•威爾遜會趁我睡著時扭斷它\N{\b0\fs12}The one you think Slade Wilson's going to break in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  類似吧\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我派遣了額外保安保護奧利弗的媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I have extra security details on Oliver's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊照看著西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Roy's keeping an eye on Thea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉和勞蕾爾在一起\N{\b0\fs12}Sara's staying close to Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我攤上了你  坐在我家門外\N{\b0\fs12}So I get you sitting outside of my house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就像大一那個曲棍球隊員一樣\N{\b0\fs12}like that lacrosse player my freshman year of college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在遇見你和奧利弗之前  我有生活的\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I had a life before you and oliver, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我只想確保你沒事  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Right. I just want to make sure you're ok, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡你這樣\N{\b0\fs12}And I love you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果斯萊德想殺了我  他就能做到\N{\b0\fs12}But if Slade wants to kill me, he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你無法阻止他\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing you can do to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回家去  好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}So go home. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,睡衣蠻好看\N{\b0\fs12}Nice jammies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}奧斯特蘭德酒店\N1141房間  馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼久才來\N{\b0\fs12}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這是搞什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在喝香檳有點早  不是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}A little early for champagne, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不覺得\N{\b0\fs12}Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛從平壤執行完任務\N{\b0\fs12}I just got back from a mission in Pyongyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\N{\b0\fs12}Well, damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是你啊\N{\b0\fs12}That was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  那是機密信息\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry. That's classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想念我的前夫  新男友\N{\b0\fs12}But I missed my ex-husband, new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,超能聯合調查組在這個酒店\N{\b0\fs12}And A.R.G.U.S. has a standing reservation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給重要人物留了一個長久房\N{\b0\fs12}at this hotel for very important assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你能留下來嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗和我遇上了...\N{\b0\fs12}Well, Oliver and I kind of have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一點事\N{\b0\fs12}situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我們在處理\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, yeah, we're handling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說能留下來\N{\b0\fs12}So you can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿富汗  坎達哈  南區指揮部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎  麥考斯\N{\b0\fs12}Is there a problem, Michaels?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}六年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要休息  女人們都累了\N{\b0\fs12}We need to rest. These women are tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都累了\N{\b0\fs12}We're all tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,距離營地還有很長的路  繼續走\N{\b0\fs12}It's a long hike back to camp. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要我去向女人們解釋\N{\b0\fs12}Shall I go explain to the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,需要在天黑前回去的原因嗎\N{\b0\fs12}ladies why they want to get back before dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她們不能和你說話\N{\b0\fs12}They're not allowed to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼  因為我是個美國人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Why, 'cause I'm an American?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你是個男人\N{\b0\fs12}Because you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休息五分鐘吧\N{\b0\fs12}Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,女人參軍  不能挺\N{\b0\fs12}Girls in the military. Can't keep up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就別進  這話真沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}don't join up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}喝不喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我的腳出問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我有件事需要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[普什圖語]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Whoa, whoa, hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你認出來了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You recognize that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該認識  \N{\b0\fs12}You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他在美軍高價值目標名單上\N{\b0\fs12}He's on the U.S. Military's high value target list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,葛雷姆•卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}Gholem Qadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,販賣鴉片的大毒梟兼軍火商\N{\b0\fs12}Opium drug lord and arms dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,務必活捉\N{\b0\fs12}Wanted alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前說參軍的女人怎麼著來著\N{\b0\fs12}What were you saying about women in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們結婚的時候為什麼沒做這些有趣的事\N{\b0\fs12}Why didn't we do fun stuff like this when we were married?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從我們繁忙的日程中\N{\b0\fs12}And take time out from our
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抽出時間把另一半搞瘋嗎\N{\b0\fs12}busy schedule of driving each other crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼達\N{\b0\fs12}Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,別一副擔心的樣子  麥考斯探員\N{\b0\fs12}Don't look so worried, Agent Michaels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都會在職業生涯的某個時間點\N{\b0\fs12}We've all availed ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,利用自己的身份來獲取一些利益\N{\b0\fs12}of the ostrander suite at some point in our careers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了一些事  跟我一起走一趟吧\N{\b0\fs12}Something's come up, I'll need you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,工作來了\N{\b0\fs12}Duty calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜也是\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其實\N{\b0\fs12}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指你們兩個\N{\b0\fs12}I meant both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在看的這個是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are we looking at here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,羥基環沙林  一種神經毒素\N{\b0\fs12}Hydroxy-cyclosarin. It's a nerve agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是一種化學武器的原型\N{\b0\fs12}It's the apocalypse in the form of a chemical weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,準備用於襲擊一處自由市場\N{\b0\fs12}And it's about to hit the open market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是超能力聯合調查組的探員們\N{\b0\fs12}A.R.G.U.S. agents uncovered
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在坎達格的一座製造工廠裡發現的\N{\b0\fs12}a manufacturing plant in Kahndaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎所有樣本都已記錄在案  除了一個\N{\b0\fs12}All samples were accounted for, except for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這段錄影在兩周之後拍攝於\N{\b0\fs12}Two weeks later, this footage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,庫拉克南部的一個偏僻村莊\N{\b0\fs12}was captured in a remote village in southern Qurac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一毫升就能殺死方圓十英里內的生物\N{\b0\fs12}One milliliter has a kill radius of ten miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而那些樣品只需要一半就能達到同等效果\N{\b0\fs12}It only took half that amount to produce these results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的線人追蹤到樣本\N{\b0\fs12}Our sources have traced the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,穿越歐洲送到了馬爾科維亞的一處地方\N{\b0\fs12}sample through Europe to an estate in Markovia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那就派軍隊去吧\N{\b0\fs12}So send in the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果派軍隊  我們的政府就要面對\N{\b0\fs12}We send in the army, we risk an international spectacle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,無法承受的國際壓力\N{\b0\fs12}our government can't afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事必須秘密處理\N{\b0\fs12}This has to be off-book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我起草強奪方案  沒問題\N{\b0\fs12}If you need me to draw up the smash and grab, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但約翰不是外勤探員  他沒有資格\N{\b0\fs12}But John isn't a field agent. He's not qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就他和奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}Judging from how he and Oliver Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在業餘時間裡做的事而言\N{\b0\fs12}spend their free time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我說他很夠格\N{\b0\fs12}I'd say his credits transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我比你更不想\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, look, I don't want this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這件事被曝光\N{\b0\fs12}thing out in the open any more than you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可不會讓\N{\b0\fs12}but I'm not sending my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我老闆再陪著你來趟商務旅行\N{\b0\fs12}boss in on another one of your business trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事我不打算扯上綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}I have no intention of involving the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你\N{\b0\fs12}I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,葛雷姆•卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}Gholem Qadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們抓到過他\N{\b0\fs12}We caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,國防部幾年前把卡迪爾放了\N{\b0\fs12}D.O.D. turned Qadir loose a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,誰想出來的好主意\N{\b0\fs12}Who thought that was a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界很複雜  約翰尼\N{\b0\fs12}It's a complicated world, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那個神經毒素不是卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}The nerve agent's not the only WMD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一想經手的大規模殺傷性武器\N{\b0\fs12}Qadir's tried getting his scummy fingers on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,上個月  他想購買馬爾科姆•梅林的\N{\b0\fs12}Last month, he tried to buy Malcolm Merlyn's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,地震機原型\N{\b0\fs12}prototype earthquake machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,順便說一下  謝謝你阻止了他\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for stopping that, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,幸運的是  他不知道你也參與了那件事\N{\b0\fs12}Fortunately, he doesn't know about your involvement in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他只記得你救過他的性命\N{\b0\fs12}He remembers you as the man who tried to save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,神經毒素被鎖住了  鑰匙在\N{\b0\fs12}The nerve agent's under lock and key
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他在馬爾科維亞的那處房產裡\N{\b0\fs12}at his estate in Markovia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,日程表顯示近期那裡會舉辦一場募捐活動\N{\b0\fs12}He's scheduled to host a fundraiser there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩個人幾乎不怎麼聯繫\N{\b0\fs12}The two of us haven't exactly kept in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我們來搞定  但是時機稍縱即逝\N{\b0\fs12}We've got that covered, but our window is rapidly closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去潛入募捐場地  把東西帶出來\N{\b0\fs12}So I infiltrate the fundraiser, come out with the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來挺簡單的\N{\b0\fs12}Sounds simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這行沒什麼是簡單的\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing in this business is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}You know that, Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\b0\fs12}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的幫助就能把毒劑帶出來\N{\b0\fs12}I don't need you to get the nerve agent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你把你的隊伍帶進去\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to get your team in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的隊伍\N{\b0\fs12}My team?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們被稱作X特遣部隊\N{\b0\fs12}They're designated "Task Force X."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,饒了我吧\N{\b0\fs12}Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼特遣部隊\N{\b0\fs12}This ain't no task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還是這麼說吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let's call it like it is--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎加入自殺小隊\N{\b0\fs12}Welcome to the suicide squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是在殘酷體罰中成長\N{\b0\fs12}"It's not only prisoners who grow course and hardened
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,並變得堅強的囚徒  還有那些\N{\b0\fs12}"from corporal punishment, but those as well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,犯下罪行和拒絕作證的人\N{\b0\fs12}who perpetrate the act or who are present to witness it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別跟他說書了\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, please stop giving him books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的作戰隊伍嗎  沃勒\N{\b0\fs12}So this is your unit, huh, Waller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,OJ和查爾斯•曼森有事不能來了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What, OJ and Charles Manson weren't available?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}O•J•辛普森  斬首謀殺其妻及一男招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}查爾斯•曼森  殘殺導演波蘭斯基孕妻及朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一次危險的行動\N{\b0\fs12}This is a dangerous operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人都具備很有用的技能\N{\b0\fs12}And these men have useful skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,任務應該有所妥協\N{\b0\fs12}Should the mission be compromised...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你寫下來吧\N{\b0\fs12}You'll just write them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,自殺小隊\N{\b0\fs12}The suicide squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟他會做出犧牲似的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, like he would ever make the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,萊拉  我不敢相信你也有份\N{\b0\fs12}Lyla, I can't believe you're on board with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人是殺人犯\N{\b0\fs12}Those men are murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那奧利弗•奎恩和莎拉•蘭斯\N{\b0\fs12}And what's the number of bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,又殺了多少人\N{\b0\fs12}between Oliver Queen and Sara Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他們做的事和我做的事  完全不同\N{\b0\fs12}What they do, what I do, is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,並不盡然  約翰  你還不明白嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Not really, John. Don't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的是你讓殺了我哥哥的傢伙\N{\b0\fs12}What I see is you letting the man who killed my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,逍遙法外\N{\b0\fs12}roam completely free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是給他自由  這是工作\N{\b0\fs12}It's not freedom. It's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是錯誤的\N{\b0\fs12}It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些小可愛需要建議嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you cuties need some counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是專業的治療師\N{\b0\fs12}I'm a trained therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"你有銷售經驗嗎"\N{\b0\fs12}"Do you have previous experience in retail?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,購物算嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does shopping count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我見過這幅表情\N{\b0\fs12}I've seen that look before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,當奧利進入生人勿進模式時  我在鏡子中的表情\N{\b0\fs12}On my face in the mirror when Ollie goes into distant mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持下去\N{\b0\fs12}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,當他準備好時  會向你敞開心扉的\N{\b0\fs12}He'll open up to you when he's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你說得沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. You'd think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我從追蹤威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}I started by tracing the donation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在莫伊拉競選中的捐款開始\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Wilson made to Moira's campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所有捐款\N{\b0\fs12}All of the money was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都經過了一系列的海外帳戶\N{\b0\fs12}routed through a series of offshore accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有一個與本地相關聯\N{\b0\fs12}None of which link back to a local address,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我查了信用卡交易記錄\N{\b0\fs12}so I looked into credit card transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-還有汽車租賃協議  -什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- and car rental agreements. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定會以某種方式四處躲藏  但不會租汽車\N{\b0\fs12}He's got to get around somehow, just not by rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德以前是情報科學學會的\N{\b0\fs12}Slade's former ASIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道如何隱藏行蹤\N{\b0\fs12}He knows how to be a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,發生搶劫事件\N{\b0\fs12}Robbery in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在第五大街和吉芬街處\N{\b0\fs12}5th and Giffen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還打擊犯罪  是吧\N{\b0\fs12}We're still in the crime fighting business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬爾科維亞  馬爾科夫堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}藝術品拍賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}藝術品拍賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先驅者已盯緊目標\N{\b0\fs12}Harbinger has eyes on the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,點燃火把\N{\b0\fs12}Light the torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手準備就緒\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot is a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,榴散彈準備就緒\N{\b0\fs12}Shrapnel's a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎準備就緒\N{\b0\fs12}Tiger's a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知更鳥\N{\b0\fs12}This is Mockingbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先驅者  你可以隨時行動\N{\b0\fs12}Harbinger, you have a green light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自由槍騎兵準備就緒了  死亡射手呢\N{\b0\fs12}Freelancer, you're a go. Deadshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,自由槍騎兵在我視野中\N{\b0\fs12}Got Freelancer in my sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不朝我開槍\N{\b0\fs12}What's stopping you from shooting me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,樂意之極\N{\b0\fs12}Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩給支香煙行嗎  我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Can I trouble you for a cigarette, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不抽煙  而且我也不是你朋友\N{\b0\fs12}I don't smoke, and I'm not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是做什麼的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What it is I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你販賣毒品  軍火  兒童\N{\b0\fs12}You're dealing drugs, weapons and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在戰爭中左右逢源\N{\b0\fs12}Play both sides of the conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖國深陷戰火  你還在撈錢\N{\b0\fs12}Make money while your country burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的人可不止我一個\N{\b0\fs12}I do not have to be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放了我  我給你榮華富貴\N{\b0\fs12}Let me go, I make you rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想收買我的人嗎  卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}You trying to bribe my men, Qadir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們想賺錢\N{\b0\fs12}If we wanted to make a buck,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就不會來這個地方  白癡\N{\b0\fs12}this is the last place we'd be, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\b0\fs12}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我沒有看到...\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry, I wasn't looking where I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,葛雷姆•卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}Gholem Qadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不敢相信\N{\b0\fs12}I do know what is less likely--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰•狄格爾會這麼笨拙\N{\b0\fs12}that John Diggle would be clumsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,世界這麼大竟然在這裡遇到你\N{\b0\fs12}or I would find him here, of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡藝術嗎  我的朋友\N{\b0\fs12}You like art, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我善於抓住好的投資機會\N{\b0\fs12}I know a good investment when I see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是退伍了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Out of the military, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還幹了個比較賺錢的行當\N{\b0\fs12}And in a more lucrative line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹的是什麼行當呢\N{\b0\fs12}What kind of work is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一個你不應該問的行當\N{\b0\fs12}The kind you don't get to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你  葛雷姆\N{\b0\fs12}It's good seeing you, Gholem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一切正常嗎  狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Everything all right here, Mr. Diggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他跟我一起的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, he's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個士兵現在還有護衛了\N{\b0\fs12}So the soldier now has his own security.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個行業中  若做得好  就會得罪人\N{\b0\fs12}In my line of work, when I do a good job, I tend to make enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好人變成壞人\N{\b0\fs12}A good man turns bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,壞人變成好人\N{\b0\fs12}Bad man turns good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你改變了我的人生\N{\b0\fs12}You changed my life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我  那不是我本意\N{\b0\fs12}Trust me, that was never my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你們的政府提供了情報\N{\b0\fs12}The intelligence I provided your government,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,保住了我的命\N{\b0\fs12}it saved many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我自由了  我會盡力做出回報\N{\b0\fs12}Now as a free man, I give back when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\b0\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\b0\fs12}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\b0\fs12}It's all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,似曾相識啊  朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Deja vu, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Qadir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\b0\fs12}I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定不是目標\N{\b0\fs12}I do not believe I was the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我所說  當我幹得好時  就會得罪人\N{\b0\fs12}Like I said, when I do my job right, I tend to make enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得走了\N{\b0\fs12}We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,幹得好  死亡射手  準備離開現場\N{\b0\fs12}Good job, Deadshot. You're a go for exfil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,正在離開\N{\b0\fs12}Already in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\b0\fs12}Except, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不止我一個人\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,榴散彈剛剛跑了\N{\b0\fs12}Shrapnel just bolted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他\N{\b0\fs12}Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,正在跟蹤他  往東去了\N{\b0\fs12}Picking him up, headed east.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,榴散彈\N{\b0\fs12}Shrapnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,停下  返回集結點\N{\b0\fs12}Stand down and return to the rally point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會加入你們高尚的軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}I won't be conscripted into your moral army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,停下  最後警告\N{\b0\fs12}Stand down! Final warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是在一個沒有引渡條約的國家\N{\b0\fs12}Especially not while in a country without an extradition treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\b0\fs12}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,榴散彈剛剛被罰出場了\N{\b0\fs12}Shrapnel just fouled out of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正準備為此吃爆米花慶祝呢\N{\b0\fs12}We're going to want popcorn for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰  你自己也說過  他們是殺人犯\N{\b0\fs12}You said it yourself, John. They're murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是罪犯\N{\b0\fs12}Criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們需要激勵來聽從命令\N{\b0\fs12}They need an incentive to follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就把炸藥裝進他的頭裡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}So you rigged their heads with explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他們守規矩就沒有危險\N{\b0\fs12}There's no danger as long as they play by the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝費爾不守規矩\N{\b0\fs12}Scheffer didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像都不認識你了  萊拉\N{\b0\fs12}It's like I don't even know you anymore, Lyla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪爾的事現在什麼情況\N{\b0\fs12}Where are we at with Qadir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,救人一命  得到一枚銀星勛章\N{\b0\fs12}Save a man's life once, get a silver star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,救人兩命  租件晚禮服吧\N{\b0\fs12}Save it twice? Rent a tux.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等待您的下一步指示  長官\N{\b0\fs12}I'll await further instructions, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}葛雷姆\N請光臨我的人道主義募捐會  已附詳情與說明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}你的人可真難搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的耐性也不多\N{\b0\fs12}So is my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你那位威爾遜先生的星城銀行帳號\N{\b0\fs12}This is Starling City Bank account number for your Mr. Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,先說好\N{\b0\fs12}To be clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿走信封後我們就兩清了\N{\b0\fs12}take this envelope and we are through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你的朋友沒興趣\N{\b0\fs12}I do not care who your friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}能達成共識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,別緊張  是我\N{\b0\fs12}Relax, it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on, Ollie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和我談談\N{\b0\fs12}Hey! Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不到時候\N{\b0\fs12}Now is not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那要等到什麼時候\N{\b0\fs12}Then when is the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要找黑手黨  你失控了\N{\b0\fs12}The Bratva, Ollie? You're losing your grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德影響了你的判斷\N{\b0\fs12}Ok? Slade's getting in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我想結束這一切\N{\b0\fs12}I need this to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我得找到他\N{\b0\fs12}And for it to stop, I need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前  你覺得你\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, and until then, how long do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人可以撐多久\N{\b0\fs12}you can keep this up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃東西  很少休息\N{\b0\fs12}You're not eating, you're barely sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只要睡下就會做噩夢\N{\b0\fs12}And when you do, you have nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你夢到她了  是不是\N{\b0\fs12}They're about her, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經盡力了\N{\b0\fs12}You did what you had to do, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃當時差點殺死了我們兩個\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo was going to shoot Shado, or me, or both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的選擇\N{\b0\fs12}It was an impossible choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但我選了\N{\b0\fs12}I made it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你沒那麼選\N{\b0\fs12}But if you had chosen differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那你每晚夢到的將會是我\N{\b0\fs12}then it would be me haunting you at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在也有危險  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}It still could be, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們得分開\N{\b0\fs12}That's why we have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他會利用你傷害我\N{\b0\fs12}He's going to use you to hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,或直接攻擊你\N{\b0\fs12}Or he's going to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我保持距離\N{\b0\fs12}Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你還沒有提起\N{\b0\fs12}Seeing as how you haven't brought it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,據我分析  我給你的線索裡\N{\b0\fs12}I'm guessing you haven't got very far
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你並沒有查到什麼\N{\b0\fs12}with that H.I.V.E. Lead I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話  做你的事\N{\b0\fs12}Just make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是這麼健談  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}You're usually so chatty, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是女人的問題嗎  她騙到你了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}These problems with your girl, they got you down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的女兒呢\N{\b0\fs12}And what about your girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在牢裡供起來的那個\N{\b0\fs12}The one you have a shrine to in that cell of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊\N{\b0\fs12}Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你女兒知道你是做什麼的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Does your daughter know what you do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我做這行的原因\N{\b0\fs12}She is why I do what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的嗎  -對\N{\b0\fs12}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一個小女孩能有多少敵人\N{\b0\fs12}How many enemies can a little girl have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我花不掉的酬勞\N{\b0\fs12}Everything I make beyond expenses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都匯進了一個保密信託\N{\b0\fs12}goes in a blind trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩最想要的是爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}A girl needs her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不會是我這個爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Nah, not this father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一能為她做的\N{\b0\fs12}Best thing I can do for her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不參與她的人生\N{\b0\fs12}not be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們花了好大力氣才給約翰\N{\b0\fs12}You know, we went through all that trouble to get Johnny here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,搞到這個破舞會的邀請函\N{\b0\fs12}invited to this little shindig.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不用就太可惜了\N{\b0\fs12}Seems like an awful waste not to use that invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你來用  一旦神經藥劑得手\N{\b0\fs12}You're using it. Once you have hands on the nerve agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就放進口袋走人\N{\b0\fs12}pocket it, walk right on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\b0\fs12}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝您的傾情贊助\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you very much. Your generosity is much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這身不是迷彩服\N{\b0\fs12}That's not exactly army camo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可你想過萬一卡迪爾認出你該怎麼辦嗎\N{\b0\fs12}But have you given any thought to what would happen if Qadir recognizes you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格先生  這是哪位美人啊\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Diggle. Who is this vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的新保鏢\N{\b0\fs12}His new bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你可得給我介紹下你的保安公司了\N{\b0\fs12}Mmm. You will have to refer me to your security company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興你今晚能前來\N{\b0\fs12}I'm glad you could come tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這遠不足以報答你對我的兩次\N{\b0\fs12}It's the least I could do after you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,救命之恩\N{\b0\fs12}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們裡面見  夥計\N{\b0\fs12}I will see you inside, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,葛雷姆\N{\b0\fs12}Gholem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎沒來得及\N{\b0\fs12}It would seem I didn't have time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我的保鏢辦理邀請函\N{\b0\fs12}to get credentials for my associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來  跟我一起\N{\b0\fs12}Come. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Gosh, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘記還有這個了\N{\b0\fs12}I forgot those were in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,盡情享受  狄格先生\N{\b0\fs12}Enjoy the benefit, Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手和裝備都到位了\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot and his gear are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎總攬全域\N{\b0\fs12}Tiger's got the overwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,全體注意  準備行動\N{\b0\fs12}Harbinger to all, fire in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,十點鐘方向有敵人\N{\b0\fs12}Shooter at my ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我掩護你\N{\b0\fs12}I got you covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好  快上\N{\b0\fs12}Bounding! Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全殲\N{\b0\fs12}All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還是個孩子\N{\b0\fs12}It's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚真漂亮\N{\b0\fs12}And don't you look lovely tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你應該和你的保鏢跳支舞\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I think you owe your bodyguard a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.53,0:24:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,請吧\N{\b0\fs12}I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.27,0:24:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手正在前去取包裹\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot en route to package.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的命運\N{\b0\fs12}The fate of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,落在佛洛德•羅通手上\N{\b0\fs12}resting in the hands of Floyd Lawton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這有利於任務\N{\b0\fs12}It helps to focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.28,0:24:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是這麼麻痹自己的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that what you tell yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.35,0:24:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會以扭曲的眼光\N{\b0\fs12}I tell myself to see the world how it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.24,0:24:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看待這個世界\N{\b0\fs12}not how I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.58,0:25:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都行走在灰色地帶\N{\b0\fs12}We both operate in the grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的差別就是  我願意承認\N{\b0\fs12}The only difference is, is I'm willing to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我們兩個唯一的差別\N{\b0\fs12}That's not the only difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.38,0:25:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對  但我不喜歡評判別人\N{\b0\fs12}That's true. I don't judge other people for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.59,0:25:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,萊拉  我還是原來的那個我\N{\b0\fs12}Lyla, I'm the same man I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒有變啊\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm who I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.08,0:25:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你太固執了  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}You're rigid, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.65,0:25:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不接受任何其他人的看法\N{\b0\fs12}You're blind to any viewpoint that isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.29,0:25:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,過去的幾個月很開心\N{\b0\fs12}These past few months have been amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.50,0:25:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們一直沉溺玩樂  而非交流\N{\b0\fs12}But we've done more playing than talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.96,0:25:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們一旦開始談  就會鬧分手\N{\b0\fs12}Because when we talk, we tend to get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.83,0:25:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心\N{\b0\fs12}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.94,0:25:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我第一次做\N{\b0\fs12}It's virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.12,0:25:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它嘗起來才那麼糟嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Ugh. Which is why it tastes terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.83,0:25:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\b0\fs12}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:25:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你和莎拉進展不錯\N{\b0\fs12}It looks like things with you and Sara are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.94,0:26:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這個話題不該和你談\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not sure you're the best person to talk to with all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.20,0:26:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為出軌  沉船  溺水\N{\b0\fs12}Is it because of the whole cheating, shipwreck, drowning,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.20,0:26:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒淹死  你回來了  她也回來了這事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}not drowning, you're back, she's back thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.36,0:26:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.95,0:26:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我說得很殘忍但也很誠實\N{\b0\fs12}It's brutal AA honesty talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.09,0:26:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我更喜歡我們相互欺騙的時候\N{\b0\fs12}I think I preferred it when we were all lying to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.29,0:26:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你只是覺得你喜歡\N{\b0\fs12}No, you just thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.77,0:26:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我幾乎比所有人都瞭解你  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}I know you better than almost anyone, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你覺得自己不配得到幸福\N{\b0\fs12}I know that you think that you don't deserve to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.39,0:26:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但你錯了\N{\b0\fs12}but you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.95,0:26:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你或許認為跟她保持一定距離\N{\b0\fs12}You may think that keeping her at arm's length,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是在保護她  但其實並不是\N{\b0\fs12}you're protecting her, but you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是在保護自己\N{\b0\fs12}You're only protecting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.84,0:26:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那麼簡單\N{\b0\fs12}It's more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.72,0:26:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,從來都不簡單\N{\b0\fs12}It always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.71,0:26:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我查到你給我的那銀行帳戶的地址了\N{\b0\fs12}I got the address for that account number you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.41,0:26:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我來叫羅伊和莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}I'll call Roy and Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.71,0:26:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不會讓斯萊德有更多目標\N{\b0\fs12}No. I'm not giving Slade any more targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.08,0:26:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能隻身前往  那是自殺\N{\b0\fs12}You can't go out there by yourself, it's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:26:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這事由我們兩人而起\N{\b0\fs12}This started with the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也要結束於我們兩人之間\N{\b0\fs12}That's how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.67,0:27:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手已就位\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot's on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.06,0:27:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\b0\fs12}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.44,0:28:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他領先太多了\N{\b0\fs12}He's too far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他花了好多年計劃這一切\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, he spent years planning this,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.88,0:28:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他知道有關我的一切\N{\b0\fs12}and he knows everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.60,0:28:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  我...\N{\b0\fs12}I can't, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎麼阻止他\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know how to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以讓別人幫你\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you start by letting people help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.12,0:29:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但他會來對付你的\N{\b0\fs12}But he's going to come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.05,0:29:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以活著...\N{\b0\fs12}You're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.35,0:29:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為莎朵死了\N{\b0\fs12}because Shado isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.96,0:29:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等他來的時候  你覺得我們倆在不在一起\N{\b0\fs12}And when he does, do you think it'll make a difference
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.85,0:29:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,會有區別嗎\N{\b0\fs12}whether or not we're together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.23,0:29:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他來吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let him come.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.28,0:29:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是他在島上認識的那個小女孩了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not the girl he knew on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.80,0:29:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒那麼容易被殺死的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not that easy to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.04,0:29:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一起面對\N{\b0\fs12}Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.54,0:29:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一起面對\N{\b0\fs12}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.62,0:30:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我進來了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.19,0:30:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,30秒後神經毒劑到手\N{\b0\fs12}I'll have the nerve agent in my pocket in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.64,0:30:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先驅者\N{\b0\fs12}Harbinger...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.38,0:30:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡出了一點小狀況\N{\b0\fs12}We've got what I would describe as a little bit of a situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.84,0:30:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,解釋清楚\N{\b0\fs12}Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.50,0:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到神經毒劑了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I got eyes on the nerve agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.60,0:30:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但我無法移動它\N{\b0\fs12}and I'm not going to be able to move it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.24,0:30:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用直接拿走了\N{\b0\fs12}much less pocket it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.62,0:30:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,原地待命  死亡射手  我要跟沃勒匯報一下\N{\b0\fs12}Stand by, Deadshot. I need to talk to Waller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.81,0:30:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知更鳥  請說\N{\b0\fs12}Go for Mockingbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們遇到麻煩了  \N{\b0\fs12}We have a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.28,0:30:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,目標比行動前指示的大很多\N{\b0\fs12}The package is much bigger than our pre-op briefing indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.81,0:30:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,原地待命\N{\b0\fs12}Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.18,0:30:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手已就位  我需要看到他所看到的\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot's on target; I need to see what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.09,0:30:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啟動他眼裡的攝像頭\N{\b0\fs12}Activate the camera in his eye piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.15,0:30:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,羅通裝備的多光譜視頻\N{\b0\fs12}Multi spectrum from Lawton's rig
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.56,0:30:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上出現\N{\b0\fs12}coming in...now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.20,0:30:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,相符\N{\b0\fs12}It's a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.45,0:31:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎  準備撤退\N{\b0\fs12}Tiger, move for extraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.17,0:31:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手  原地不動\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot, remain in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.82,0:31:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,先驅者和自由槍騎兵  撤退到集合點\N{\b0\fs12}Harbinger and Freelancer, evac and head to the rally point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡射手還沒有帶著東西上來\N{\b0\fs12}Deadshot still isn't topside with the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.81,0:31:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要看到罷了  撤到集合點\N{\b0\fs12}I only needed eyes on. Fall back to the rally point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.00,0:31:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你早知道神經毒劑太大不能帶走嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Wait...you knew that the nerve agent was too large to be extracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.91,0:31:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退到集合點\N{\b0\fs12}Fall back to the rally point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,九號已準備好\N{\b0\fs12}Nine is inbound and hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,知更鳥撤出\N{\b0\fs12}Mockingbird out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.92,0:31:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,九號是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell are Nines?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.99,0:31:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,MQ九號  劫掠者\N{\b0\fs12}Mq-9s. Predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沃勒發動了無人機襲擊\N{\b0\fs12}Waller's called in a drone strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,十分鐘之內  這裡的所有人都會死\N{\b0\fs12}Everyone here is dead inside of ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.22,0:31:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,九號裝載著地獄火導彈\N{\b0\fs12}The Nines carry the hellfire missile.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一枚就足以把這棟大樓夷為平地\N{\b0\fs12}Just one of them can level this whole building.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.65,0:31:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你老闆不在乎會把誰炸死\N{\b0\fs12}And your boss doesn't care who's here when it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.44,0:31:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,萊拉  我們得把這些人弄出去\N{\b0\fs12}Lyla, we have to get these people out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.29,0:31:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我們可以啟動房屋警報\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe there's a house alarm we can trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.53,0:31:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,約翰  我們必須要走了\N{\b0\fs12}John, we have to move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.56,0:32:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個更好的主意\N{\b0\fs12}I have a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.19,0:32:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.67,0:32:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.03,0:32:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家注意\N{\b0\fs12}Can I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.58,0:32:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝我們的主辦人\N{\b0\fs12}In honor of our host.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.57,0:32:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,葛雷姆•卡迪爾擅長做一切他決心要做的事\N{\b0\fs12}Gholem Qadir excels at everything he puts his mind to,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.64,0:32:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,生意\N{\b0\fs12}be it business,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.26,0:32:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,慈善\N{\b0\fs12}philanthropy...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.12,0:32:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或者恐怖主義事業\N{\b0\fs12}or terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.45,0:32:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得葛雷姆是一個文藝復興式的人物\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I guess you could say gholem is somewhat of a renaissance man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.66,0:32:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他在每個領域都涉足一點\N{\b0\fs12}He dabbles in a little bit of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.60,0:32:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,比如說軍火交易  我說性交易了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Like arms trading-- did I mention the sex trafficking?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.63,0:32:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,還有他手裡的致命神經毒劑\N{\b0\fs12}Or the deadly nerve agent that he's holding
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.19,0:32:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這舞池下面10米的地方\N{\b0\fs12}just 30 feet beneath this very dance floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.59,0:32:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是謊話  這個人是雇傭兵\N{\b0\fs12}These are lies! This man is a mercenary!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.39,0:32:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,勞頓\N{\b0\fs12}Lawton!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有回答  我得去幫他\N{\b0\fs12}He's not answering. I have to go help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.80,0:32:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信我剛說了這些\N{\b0\fs12}I can't believe I just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.24,0:32:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你五年前也在阿富汗\N{\b0\fs12}You! You were in Afghanistan five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.79,0:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你和那個叛徒從一開始就在騙我\N{\b0\fs12}You and that Judas have been deceiving me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.01,0:33:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來得正好\N{\b0\fs12}Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的邀請涵遲遲不來  等煩了\N{\b0\fs12}Got tired of waiting for my invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,違抗命令了啊  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}Disobeying orders, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.67,0:33:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小心身後\N{\b0\fs12}Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.52,0:33:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠我兩個人情了  \N{\b0\fs12}That's two you owe me, junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.35,0:33:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得走了\N{\b0\fs12}We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.78,0:33:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沃勒讓我待在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Waller told me to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.15,0:33:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,無人機馬上就會來襲了\N{\b0\fs12}There's an incoming drone strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.86,0:33:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真及時  讓你的隊員都出去\N{\b0\fs12}How contemporary. Get your team clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我的隊員之一\N{\b0\fs12}You are on my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.41,0:33:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你該離開了\N{\b0\fs12}And it's time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.89,0:33:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  說得對  是時候了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, that's right. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.26,0:33:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我離開的方式\N{\b0\fs12}And this is my way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.03,0:33:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自殺小隊  記得嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Suicide squad, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.35,0:33:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可有可無  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}I'm expendable, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.51,0:33:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我腦中那顆該死的炸彈也能證明這一點\N{\b0\fs12}Even got the damn bomb in my head to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣  我至少做了件光榮的事\N{\b0\fs12}This way, at least I get to go out doing something honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.12,0:33:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能死得這麼容易  羅通\N{\b0\fs12}You don't get to die that easy, Lawton.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.72,0:34:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.81,0:34:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那你給我一個\N{\b0\fs12}Why don't you give me even just
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不這麼做的理由\N{\b0\fs12}one good reason why not, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.75,0:34:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊\N{\b0\fs12}Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.49,0:34:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-那神經毒氣怎麼辦  -相信我\N{\b0\fs12}- What about the nerve gas? - Believe me--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.12,0:34:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沃勒已經都搞定了\N{\b0\fs12}Waller's already got that covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.25,0:34:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快走  快快快\N{\b0\fs12}Go, go, go, go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.65,0:34:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,無人機改變飛行路線了  現在正跟著我們\N{\b0\fs12}The drone shifted course. It's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.05,0:34:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得很好笑嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you find that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.24,0:34:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女人真厲害啊\N{\b0\fs12}Whoa. What a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你們覺得她是怎麼知道把無人機派去哪裡的\N{\b0\fs12}How do you think she knew where to send the drone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.55,0:34:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說確切的坐標地點\N{\b0\fs12}And I mean, the precise coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:35:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-移植追蹤器  -炸彈和GPS\N{\b0\fs12}- The implants. - Bomb and GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.17,0:35:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很聰明對吧\N{\b0\fs12}Pretty clever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.65,0:35:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,無人機的目標不是葛雷姆的房子\N{\b0\fs12}The drone ain't targeting Gholem's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.88,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而是我\N{\b0\fs12}It's targeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.95,0:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  不該先問問我的意見嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Whoa, hang on, do I get a say in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-轉身  -你幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- Turn around. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.14,0:35:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我寧願被炸飛\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I think I'd rather get blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.09,0:35:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,穩住  會很疼的\N{\b0\fs12}Hold still. This is going to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.65,0:35:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科夫政府威脅說要報復\N{\b0\fs12}The Markovian government is threatening retaliation
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.68,0:35:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在禁飛區無緣無故出動無人機襲擊\N{\b0\fs12}following an unprovoked drone attack over a no-fly zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.25,0:36:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不就是想避免這種局面嗎  做得漂亮啊\N{\b0\fs12}Just the attention we wanted to avoid. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.69,0:36:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我派無人機去的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not the one who sent that drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,無人機隱身了  化學武器藏匿點\N{\b0\fs12}It was cloaked. An explosion atop
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.78,0:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上面的爆炸是很容易解釋的\N{\b0\fs12}a chemical weapons cache is easy to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.32,0:36:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  還有目擊者  所以我們\N{\b0\fs12}Instead, there were witnesses and we had
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.93,0:36:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還得派海豹突擊隊去清理現場\N{\b0\fs12}to send in a seal team to clean out the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.36,0:36:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你拉我幫你幹什麼不幹凈的勾當時\N{\b0\fs12}I guess you'll think twice before dragging me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就應該三思而後行  沃勒\N{\b0\fs12}in to do your dirty work, Waller.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.20,0:36:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不覺得這是個問題\N{\b0\fs12}Somehow I don't think it will be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣  狄格爾先生\N{\b0\fs12}Good day, Mr. Diggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.32,0:36:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思議啊\N{\b0\fs12}Kind of uncanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.20,0:36:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾怎麼知道羅通的追蹤器在什麼地方\N{\b0\fs12}How Diggle knew exactly where Lawton's implant was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.96,0:36:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總之\N{\b0\fs12}Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.77,0:36:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這暴露出了一個明顯的設計缺陷\N{\b0\fs12}it exposed an obvious design flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.02,0:36:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,以後把追蹤器植入到脊椎裡吧\N{\b0\fs12}We'll be putting in the implants in their spinal vertebrae now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.19,0:36:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,讓羅通跟其他人準備手術\N{\b0\fs12}Have Lawton and the others prepped for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.97,0:36:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沃勒說幾年後你可能會得到赦免\N{\b0\fs12}Waller said in a few years, you might even get a pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}Don't worry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.23,0:37:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會活那麼久的  你我心知肚明\N{\b0\fs12}We both know I'm not going to be around that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.83,0:37:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒被解雇嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You still employed?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我這種權限級別的人沒那麼容易\N{\b0\fs12}People with my security clearance aren't that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.85,0:37:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-就擺脫的  -對\N{\b0\fs12}- to get rid of. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.38,0:37:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們呢  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}What about us, Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚殺我弟弟的那個人\N{\b0\fs12}Last night, the man who killed my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.20,0:37:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,比要保護全世界的那個女人\N{\b0\fs12}showed more character than the woman charged
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.27,0:37:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,更加高尚\N{\b0\fs12}with protecting the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.70,0:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是非好壞的界限已經沒那麼明顯了\N{\b0\fs12}Good and bad is not so clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.67,0:37:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有一件事我非常確定\N{\b0\fs12}One thing I do know for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,黑白分明那麼確定\N{\b0\fs12}black and white...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:37:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我不能再失去你了\N{\b0\fs12}is that I can't ever lose you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.42,0:38:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,終於\N{\b0\fs12}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.84,0:38:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也達成一致了\N{\b0\fs12}Something we agree on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.13,0:38:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又多了一個原先是恐怖分子的盟友\N{\b0\fs12}Well, there goes another terrorist-turned-ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.29,0:38:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  我推薦你\N{\b0\fs12}By the way, I put you in for a commendation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.48,0:38:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去救卡迪爾了\N{\b0\fs12}for saving Qadir's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,記得請我喝酒\N{\b0\fs12}You owe me a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.70,0:38:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\b0\fs12}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.96,0:38:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  殺個孩子得到勛章  對吧\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, well, kill a kid, get a medal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.73,0:38:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那個人拿卡拉希步槍朝你射擊\N{\b0\fs12}When someone's shooting a kalishnikov at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.57,0:38:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就不是個孩子\N{\b0\fs12}he's not a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.61,0:38:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不這麼認為\N{\b0\fs12}I see things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.90,0:38:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,世界很複雜  約翰\N{\b0\fs12}It's a complicated world, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.32,0:38:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以叫你約翰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is it OK if I call you Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.38,0:38:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像還不知道你的名字  麥考斯\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think I caught your first name, Michaels.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.17,0:38:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,萊拉\N{\b0\fs12}Lyla.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.54,0:39:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很高興認識你  萊拉\N{\b0\fs12}It's really good to meet you, Lyla.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.44,0:39:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,下面是國際新聞  一支聯合國巡查隊\N{\b0\fs12}In international news, a United Nations inspections team
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.02,0:39:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為藏在人道主義者葛雷姆•卡迪爾\N{\b0\fs12}was called to a chemical weapons manufacturing facility
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.16,0:39:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科夫莊園下的\N{\b0\fs12}hidden beneath the Markovian estate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,化學武器生產製造設施而出動\N{\b0\fs12}of humanitarian Gholem Qadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.36,0:39:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,星城新聞  市長候選人莫伊拉•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}Closer to home, mayoral candidate Moira Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.92,0:39:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在各地進行演說\N{\b0\fs12}stumped for an initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.55,0:39:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,企圖在學校游泳池建造項目後再復興市中心\N{\b0\fs12}to revive inner city after school swim programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得自己的孩子小時候\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I remember how much my children
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.66,0:39:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有多麼喜歡游泳\N{\b0\fs12}enjoyed swimming when they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.53,0:39:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在泳池里拉都拉不出來\N{\b0\fs12}I couldn't get them out of the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要...\N{\b0\fs12}We need--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.70,0:39:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你不喜歡游泳\N{\b0\fs12}I thought you hated swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.14,0:39:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨游泳\N{\b0\fs12}I detest swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.37,0:39:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭也是\N{\b0\fs12}So does Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.71,0:39:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候我母親\N{\b0\fs12}My mother sometimes--ahem--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.62,0:39:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那麼喜歡真相\N{\b0\fs12}enjoys a casual relationship with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,總之\N{\b0\fs12}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.01,0:40:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你在這裡陪我\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for being there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.66,0:40:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說不讓你把我推開嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You mean for not letting you push me away?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.91,0:40:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再那樣了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.69,0:40:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那就好\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.61,0:40:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也是在浪費自己的時間\N{\b0\fs12}You'll be wasting your time, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.81,0:40:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你聽從我的建議了\N{\b0\fs12}It looks like you took my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.94,0:40:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.51,0:40:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我跟莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Helping me with Sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.57,0:40:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  這樣做不容易\N{\b0\fs12}I know that that... can't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.54,0:40:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,幫兩個我在乎的人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Helping two people I care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.50,0:40:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有比這更容易的事了\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.45,0:40:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來帶莎拉去吃飯的\N{\b0\fs12}I came by to take Sara to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.31,0:40:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想一起去吃嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Would you care to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.58,0:40:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想去  但是得先去見個老朋友\N{\b0\fs12}I'd love to, but I need to go see an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.52,0:40:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.88,0:41:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.83,0:41:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  阿曼達\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Amanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.32,0:41:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還生我的氣嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Still mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.58,0:41:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,算你走運  你不在我的名單之上了\N{\b0\fs12}Lucky for you, You've been pushed down that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.15,0:41:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎  跟我相比你更加想殺的人是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Really? Who do you want to kill more than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.04,0:41:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜還活著\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.41,0:41:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他殺了\N{\b0\fs12}You killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.87,0:41:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能還活著的\N{\b0\fs12}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.94,0:41:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要跟斯萊德有關  一切皆有可能\N{\b0\fs12}Everything is possible where Slade is concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.66,0:41:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你幫我找到他\N{\b0\fs12}And I need your help to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可能有線索  -什麼線索\N{\b0\fs12}- I might have something. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.78,0:41:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直追蹤的一個人  是個雇傭兵\N{\b0\fs12}There's a new player we've been tracking-- mercenary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.21,0:41:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他所到之處屍體遍地\N{\b0\fs12}He's left a trail of bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.51,0:41:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從澳門到伊斯坦布爾再到里斯本\N{\b0\fs12}from Macau to Istanbul to Lisbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.51,0:41:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最後到了星城\N{\b0\fs12}A trail that leads right here to Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.84,0:41:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直叫他喪鐘\N{\b0\fs12}We've been calling him Deathstroke.